summary:
This is my first house which I have made.
You can find it at the Western Watchtower of Whiterun.
It would be nice if you could left a comment how do you find it or for some ideas.
descriptionHtml:
You can find this objects in the house:

1. Alchemy Table
2. Enchanting Table
3. Four barrels and three chests two sacks (nothing in the barrels in one chest there are all keys)
4. Two bookcases 
5. One noble bed
6. Grindstone
7. Armor Workbench

And please if your are have plans with my file for example change something an reupload it 
let me know it

May I will ad a garden, cellar and a smith
